- **Total Debt Items:** [N]
- **Estimated Principal (Fix Effort):** [X story points / hours]
- **Estimated Annual Interest:** [Y hours lost per year to debt]
- **Debt Ratio:** [Principal / (Principal + Codebase Value)] — [Healthy if < 20%]
- **Strategic Debt:** [N items]
- **Accidental Debt:** [N items]

## Debt Distribution by Category
| Category | Count | Principal | Interest | Priority |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Code Smells & Anti-patterns | | | | |
| Hacks & Shortcuts | | | | |
| Design Debt | | | | |
| Test Debt | | | | |
| Documentation Debt | | | | |
| Infrastructure Debt | | | | |
| **Total** | | | | |

## Debt Distribution by Module
| Module | Items | Principal | Interest |
|---|---|---|---|
| [module/path] | [N] | [hours] | [hours/year] |

## Critical Debt Items (Must Fix)

### DEBT-001: [Title]
- **Category:** [Code Smell / Hack / Design / Test / Docs / Infrastructure]
- **Type:** Strategic / Accidental
- **Location:** `path/to/file:line`
- **Description:** [What the debt is]
- **Why It's Debt:** [Why it's a problem]
- **Interest:** [Ongoing cost — slower development, bugs, confusion]
